'''法兹勒·拉合曼·汗''' （{{lang-bn|ফজলুর রহমান খান}}， {{lang-en|Fazlur Rahman Khan}}，{{bd|1929年|4月3日|1982年|3月27日}} ），[[孟加拉族|孟加拉裔]][[美国人|美国]]<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/316259/Fazlur-R-Khan |title=Fazlur R. Khan (American engineer) - Encyclopædia Britannica |encyclopedia=Britannica.com |access-date=22 December 2013 |archive-date=2014-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019000136/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/316259/Fazlur-R-Khan |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[结构工程|结构工程师]]和[[建筑师|建筑师]]，发明了[[摩天大楼|摩天大楼]]的许多重要结构，<ref name="Ali Mir 2001">{{cite book |last=Mir |first=Ali |date=2001 |title=Art of the Skyscraper: the Genius of Fazlur Khan |publisher=Rizzoli International Publications |isbn=0-8478-2370-9}}</ref><ref name="lehigh.edu">{{cite web |url=http://www.lehigh.edu/~infrk/2011.08.article.html |title=Lehigh University: Fazlur Rahman Khan Distinguished Lecture Series |publisher=Lehigh.edu |date= |access-date=22 December 2013 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701122344/https://www.lehigh.edu/~infrk/2011.08.article.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>被认为是高层建筑的“[[核心筒|筒结构]]之父” 。{{sfn|Weingardt|2005|p=75}} 他还是[[计算机辅助设计|计算机辅助设计]]（CAD）的先驱。

作为 [[SOM建築設計事務所|SOM建築設計事務所]]在芝加哥的合伙人，他比其他人更加拥抱和迎接20世纪下半叶摩天大楼建造的复兴。 {{sfn|Weingardt|2005|pp=78–}}<ref name="Designing 'cities in the sky'">[http://www4.lehigh.edu/news/newsarticle.aspx?Channel=%2FChannels%2FNews%3A+2007&WorkflowItemID=0bed2560-462b-4bd9-b834-4b5a1e91cc54 Designing 'cities in the sky'] {{Wayback|url=http://www4.lehigh.edu/news/newsarticle.aspx?Channel=%2FChannels%2FNews%3A+2007&WorkflowItemID=0bed2560-462b-4bd9-b834-4b5a1e91cc54 |date=20150701115533 }}. Lehigh University, Engineering & Applied Science. Retrieved on 26 June 2012.</ref> 因对结构系统的创新，他被誉为“结构工程领域的爱因斯坦”和“20世纪最伟大的结构工程师”，他的创新今天仍然是现代摩天大楼设计和建造的基础。<ref name="Ali Mir 2001" /><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Weingardt |first=Richard |date=February 2011 |title=Fazlur Rahman Khan: The Einstein of Structural Engineering |url=http://www.structuremag.org/?p=4704 |journal=Structure Magazine |publisher=National Council of Structural Engineers Associations |issue= |page=44 |access-date=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020051533/https://www.structuremag.org/?p=4704 |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[世界高層建築與都市人居學會|世界高層建築與都市人居學會]]设立了[[CTBUH摩天大楼奖|CTBUH摩天大楼奖]]法兹勒·汗终身成就奖章以表彰他的贡献。

他的作品包括[[世界最高樓列表|世界最高楼]]（1973年至1998年）[[威利斯大厦|威利斯大厦]]，和100层的[[約翰·漢考克中心|約翰·漢考克中心]]。除了摩天大楼，其他作品包括[[阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹国王国际机场|阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹国王国际机场]]，[[麦克梅斯-皮尔斯太阳望远镜|麦克梅斯-皮尔斯太阳望远镜]]和一些体育场。<ref name="Lynn S.Beadle pays tribute to Khan">{{cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vD0rAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA153&lpg=PA153&dq=lynn+beadle+fazlur+khan#v=onepage |title=Lynn S.Beadle pays tribute to Khan |date=27 March 1982 |access-date=18 June 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lehigh.edu/~infrk/2011.08.article.html |title=Lehigh University: Fazlur Rahman Khan Distinguished Lecture Series |publisher=Lehigh.edu |date= |access-date=18 June 2014 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701122344/https://www.lehigh.edu/~infrk/2011.08.article.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

